        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://lean-lang.org/doc/reference/latest//Tactic-Proofs/Tactic-Reference/#refine\">https://lean-lang.org/doc/reference/latest//Tactic-Proofs/Tactic-Reference/#refine</a></p>\n<p>It's like <code>exact</code>, but turns missing sub-expressions into goals.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I am not able to use it in the game apparently</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yeah, it has a lot of silly restrictions. You can try to induct on <code>nk</code> though, since <code>.recOn</code> is essentially the induction principle for the <code>≤</code> relation.</p>",
